ORG 0
MVI A       ; Load Hex 'A' (10) into AC
OUT 2       ; Send to Port 2 (Printer)
MVI B       ; Load Hex 'B' (11) into AC
OUT 2       ; Send to Port 2 (Printer)
MVI C       ; Load Hex 'C' (12) into AC
OUT 3       ; Send to Port 3 (Network)
MVI D       ; Load Hex 'D' (13) into AC
OUT 3       ; Send to Port 3 (Network)
HLT         ; Halt System